item.title: Israel, Ezekiel 38, and the End Times: How Prophecy Unfolds Before Our Eyes ????✝️
item.description: Steve Miller’s interview is a must-watch for anyone eager to understand how today’s global events align with biblical prophecy and God’s ultimate plan! ???????? He unpacks the significance of Israel's role in the end times, highlighting Ezekiel 38's prophecy about alliances forming against Israel and the rise of global unrest. Steve also dives deep into Revelation's mysteries, explaining the 144,000 Jewish witnesses and Jesus' harvest of the earth with His sickle... Feed: https://anchor.fm/s/24800588/podcast/rss
